Special Events Appearance
in Site Mechanics, Design and Development
The changing on the logo to celebrate special events, for example, putting a christmas hat instead of the crown around christmas or the bunny ears around easter.
This may be an option in the 'settings' area to enable or disable in case some people may get offended.
